FORMAT: 1A

# Nexio IMDb API

Internal, non-commercial IMDb dataset API for Nexio providing ratings and title search.

Every `/v1/*` route requires an API key via `X-API-Key` or `Authorization: Bearer`.
Authenticated routes can return `401` for missing or invalid keys, `429` when the per-key rate limit is exceeded, and `500` for unexpected server faults.

# Group Platform

## Health Check [/healthz]

### Get Health [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (HealthResponse)

